headline.main: SUBMARINE PREYS ON SWEDISH SHIP; Destroyer Attacks Raider as Torpedo Misses Freighter in Territorial Waters

lead_paragraph: STOCKHOLM, Sweden, July 2 -- The undersea warfare in the Baltic was heightened today when a submarine of unidentified nationality attacked the Swedish cargo ship Galeon and was in its turn attacked by a Swedish destroyer.
abstract: Lapse in shipments to Sweden noted
